author: johnh
msg: Reintroduce Closure Compiler to Shindig, and implement Java 1.5/1.6-specific JsCompiler bindings.
This CL reintroduces a Closure-based JsCompiler implementation, and uses Paul Lindner's Maven work to ensure
that it can be built for deployments utilizing Java 1.6. Java 1.5 gracefully falls back to the build-time compilation mechanism
in ExportJsCompiler, which does not depend on a 1.6-specific package.
